data.description: This beautiful home features 4 beds, 2.5 baths, a spacious kitchen with plenty of counter space, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining. Spacious master suite on ground floor provides comfort and convenience. Open kitchen and dining area is ideal for gathering with family and friends. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, giving everyone plenty of space. ***Home comes with solar panels, no lease simply enjoy saving on electricity. Amazing community to live in! Amenities include swimming pool with splash pad, tennis courts, covered basketball court, pavilion, multiple playgrounds, walking trails, gym, and lake. Don't miss out! Schedule your tour today!
